d:linear-gradient(135deg, #34A853, #34A853)\">Z</span><span>ZiQia.cc · <!-- -->2024-12-01<!-- --> · <!-- -->1 分钟阅读</span></div></div><div class=\"prose prose-neutral max-w-none dark:prose-invert\"><h2>背景</h2>\n<p>React Server Components（RSC）是 React 的全新架构。</p>\n<div class=\"group relative my-6\"><div class=\"shiki-light\"><pre class=\"shiki github-light\" style=\"background-color:#fff;color:#24292e\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">async</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\"> function</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\"> Posts</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">() {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">  const</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5\"> posts</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\"> await</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\"> db.</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">query</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">(</span><span style=\"color:#032F62\">'posts'</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">  return</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\"> &#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1\">ul</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">>{posts.map((p) => &#x3C;li key</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">=</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">{p.id}</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">></span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">{p.title}</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">&#x3C;/</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">li</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">></span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">)}</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">&#x3C;/</span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">ul</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49\">></span><span style=\"color:#24292E\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#24292E\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><div class=\"shiki-dark hidden\"><pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#F97583\">async</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\"> function</span><span style=\"color:#B392F0\"> Posts</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">() {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#F97583\">  const</span><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\"> posts</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\"> await</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> db.</span><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">query</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">(</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">'posts'</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#F97583\">  return</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\"> &#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">ul</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">>{posts.map((p) => &#x3C;li key</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">{p.id}</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\">></span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">{p.title}</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\">&#x3C;/</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">li</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\">></span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">)}</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\">&#x3C;/</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">ul</span><span style=\"color:#F97583\">></span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"absolute right-3 top-3 rounded-md border border-outline-variant bg-surface/90 px-2 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-on-surface-variant backdrop-blur transition-colors hover:bg-surface-variant\">Copy</button><style>\n        :root:not(.dark) .shiki-dark { display: none; }\n        :root:not(.dark) .shiki-light { display: block; }\n        .dark .shiki-dark { display: block; }\n        .dark .shiki-light { display: none; }\n      </style></div>\n<h2>工作原理</h2>\n<p>RSC 在服务器端渲染、传输到客户端后永不重渲染。</p>\n<h3>序列化格式</h3>\n<p>使用 React Flight 协议。</p>\n<h2>总结</h2>\n<p>RSC 把数据流推向服务器。</p></div><nav class=\"mt-12 flex justify-between gap-4 border-t border-outline-variant pt-6\"><a class=\"text-sm\" href=\"/cn/posts/rust-memory/\"><span class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">上一篇</span><span class=\"block font-bold\">Rust 内存模型浅析</span></a><a class=\"text-right text-sm\" href=\"/cn/posts/ai-coding-cli-tools-comparison/\"><span class=\"text-on-surface-variant\">下一篇</span><span class=\"block font-bold\">五大 AI 编程 CLI 工具横评：OpenCode、Claude Code、Codex CLI 怎么选？</span></a></nav></article><aside class=\"sticky top-24 hidden max-h-[calc(100vh-7rem)] overflow-auto lg:block\"><div class=\"mb-3 font-heading text-sm font-bold text-on-surface-variant\">目录</div><nav class=\"space-y-1 text-sm\"><a href=\"#背景\" class=\"block border-l-2 py-1 transition-colors pl-3 border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface\">背景</a><a href=\"#工作原理\" class=\"block border-l-2 py-1 transition-colors pl-3 border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface\">工作原理</a><a href=\"#序列化格式\" class=\"block border-l-2 py-1 transition-colors pl-5 border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface\">序列化格式</a><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"block border-l-2 py-1 transition-colors pl-3 border-outline-variant text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface\">总结</a></nav></aside></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"flex items-center justify-center border-t border-outline-variant px-5 py-6 text-sm text-on-surface-variant md:px-10\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> ZiQia.cc</p></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/310vm2bl3xxpt.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7738,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2offyj585lm1g.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/2offyj585lm1g.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_